{"tid":433100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前解放軍成「爆竊專家」　出獄即再犯　認罪候判","createTime":"2017-10-12T05:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T08:11:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fc9a145f427457fdb0b21071c53e02548ce158","tid":433100,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171012/s00001/96395d66f24c4497a45dac9b77bf57df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171012%2Fs00001%2F96395d66f24c4497a45dac9b77bf57df.jpg&h=cd39278a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年輕時曾任解放軍及公安的62歲男子，移居香港後曾被裁定干犯多項爆竊案件罪成，被當時的法官稱為「爆竊專家」，判囚7年。「爆竊專家」於去年7月出獄當天即重施故技，到工廠大廈爆竊，及後被捕。他今於區域法院承認入屋犯法、企圖入屋犯法，外出時備有偷竊工具等7罪，案件押至本月30日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指出，被告朱書龍（62歲）於2013年被判監，惟他出獄當天即干犯本案首控罪，即到屯門一工廠大廈爆竊。及後被告多次到港九新界不同地區的工廈犯案，辯方直言被告是專業的爆竊慣犯。<br />\n<br />\n惟辯方指出，被告教育水平低，他高中畢業後在內地曾任解放軍及公安各一年，及後於1980年來港，曾有一段婚姻及育有一子，但他已與前妻及兒子失去聯絡。辯方稱，被告出獄後居於深水埗，沒有收入，亦沒有家人支持。<br />\n<br />\n辯方強調，被告一共偷取了約2萬元現金，而相關工廈單位的事後維修費約為3萬元，且被告只是單獨犯案，認為今次只屬小型爆竊，請求輕判。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，被告於2016年7月9日到屯門一工廈的某單位爆竊並偷去多封利市封，利市封內共有1萬元。及後他亦到新浦崗、荃灣及柴灣的工廈犯案，閉路電視拍下被告的犯案過程，被告同年8月在住所附近被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171012/s00001/1507785760325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171012%2Fs00001%2F1507785760325&d=x7MGXgOW72Kzxyel2SOqzEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=409c321c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171012%2Fs00001%2F1507785760325&h=f61e3347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171012/s00001/1507785760325</a>"},{"pid":"89f1aa559e7ce8247b4d05ba4e4a3a997fb121c0","tid":433100,"uid":5026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"輸入專材<br />\n爆竊專家"},{"pid":"855dca33638f96c8dfec3b5f0bed785730a603c5","tid":433100,"uid":73,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"特登嘅<br />\n入返去有人養"},{"pid":"4f8d58349bca55e898b9824f14afbc99be340152","tid":433100,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輸入專材<br />\n爆竊專家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我估係80年抵壘政策時抵港，唔係中共殖入喎"},{"pid":"c3990c48231c4823a33b6da0b032f989801abeea","tid":433100,"uid":52423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:11:24.000Z","msg":"2013年被判7年監，2016年中就可以出獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e1996fe7e8c4c9c2417a99e13439a1674af6e8","tid":433100,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2013年被判7年監，2016年中就可以出獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有分別嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119c19c8e70f32f7be2469d98ede7fa5b967c8b8","tid":433100,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"就係呢D低汁支那人令香港變臭港！<br />\n死返支那啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d93dae4ee5ffd3b717cf9cb4dab3adb7c91f2f3","tid":433100,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2013年被判7年監，2016年中就可以出獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有分別嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /